                          <td><span class="style7"><em>Pigeons</em></span> has been featured on CBS Sunday Morning, two-dozen national and regional Public Radio programs, favorably reviewed by the New York Times (twice), Esquire Magazine, Time, Audubon, Boston Globe, Philadelphia Inquirer, and Salon, and chosen by Border Books for its Original Voices program.</td>
